== 慈善捐助 ==
自2013年，谜幻乐队捐助泰勒·罗宾逊基金会，以帮助年轻人与對抗癌症<ref>[http://kdvr.com/2014/03/17/local-kids-meet-imagine-dragons/ "Local kids meet Imagine Dragons | FOX31 Denver"] {{Wayback|url=http://kdvr.com/2014/03/17/local-kids-meet-imagine-dragons/ |date=20190512221554 }}.</ref>。

谜幻乐队也與做正确的事：停止暴力全國运动<ref>[http://www.dtwt.org/imaginedragons/imagine-dragons "Imagine Dragons Meet & Greet Benefit — Do The Write Thing: Help Stop the Violence (National Campaign to Stop Violence)"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dtwt.org/imaginedragons/imagine-dragons |date=20190616170645 }}.</ref>、国际特赦组织「把人权带回家」<ref>[http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5862633/amnesty-international-benefit-show-barclays-lineup "Imagine Dragons, The Flaming Lips to Play Amnesty International Benefit Show"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5862633/amnesty-international-benefit-show-barclays-lineup |date=20201114182034 }}.</ref>和Crackle公司的Playing It Forward影片（第一季第二集）合作<ref>[http://www.crackle.com/c/playing-it-forward "Watch Playing It Forward Online Free"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.crackle.com/c/playing-it-forward |date=20150808070557 }}.</ref>。  

在2015年，谜幻乐队发發單曲“我是我”，其所有收益全部捐给One4项目，以帮助逃亡的难民，特别是在中东地区的逃亡难民<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/theopriestley/2015/10/12/sap-apple-and-imagine-dragons-collaborate-to-support-refugee-humanitarian-project/ |title=SAP, Apple and Imagine Dragons Collaborate To Support Refugee Humanitarian Project |accessdate=2015-12-13 |archive-date=2020-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122181923/https://www.forbes.com/sites/theopriestley/2015/10/12/sap-apple-and-imagine-dragons-collaborate-to-support-refugee-humanitarian-project/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

